OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson has said
OL,8,FJeffrey Donaldson is "guilty of
OL,9,Fabusing the trust" of those within the
OL,10,Fparty with "lies and his cover-ups" in
OL,11,Frelation to his sexual crimes.
OL,13,FMr Robinson said party members were
OL,14,F"shocked" by the "filthy and vile"
OL,15,Fdescriptions of Donaldson's actions
OL,16,Fduring the trial at Newry Crown Court,
OL,17,Fin which the former DUP leader was
OL,18,Ffound guilty of 18 historical sexual
OL,19,Foffences against two women when they
OL,20,Fwere children.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@RO]rD@LOUrD@cO]vD@AOUvD@IO]vD@
OL,26,AROUvD@bO]
