OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FWhen the allegations came to light in
OL,8,F2024, Donaldson was suspended from the
OL,9,Fparty, before Mr Robinson ` then
OL,10,Fdeputy leader ` took over his role.
OL,12,FThe shocking change in leadership came
OL,13,Fjust weeks after Donaldson had led his
OL,14,Fparty back into the devolved
OL,15,Finstitutions at Stormont, having
OL,16,Fstruck a deal with the UK Government
OL,17,Fto end his two-year boycott of
OL,18,Fpowersharing in Northern Ireland in
OL,19,Fprotest at post-Brexit trading
OL,20,Farrangements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
