OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782224342
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FDonaldson had been the MP for Lagan
OL,8,FValley since 1997 and was one of the
OL,9,Fleading voices in political unionism
OL,10,Ffor more than two decades.
OL,12,FSpeaking to reporters at the Stormont
OL,13,Fhotel in Belfast, Mr Robinson welcomed
OL,14,Fthat justice had been done, describing
OL,15,Fhis predecessor's crimes as "heinous
OL,16,Fand despicable".
OL,26,@wD@]OUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
