CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782224342
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Our thoughts are first and foremost
OL,8,Fwith those innocent victims whose
OL,9,Flives have been impacted and blighted
OL,10,Fby (Donaldson's) predatory and
OL,11,Frepugnant behaviour," he said.
OL,13,F"What they have been put through, from
OL,14,Fthe initial abuse through to the
OL,15,Fimpact of having to give evidence and
OL,16,Fthe inevitable traumatisation, has
OL,17,Fbeen wicked.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@UO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
