PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782224342
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"The impact on the victims of having
OL,8,Fto come forward and to be forced by
OL,9,Ftheir perpetrators' denials to give
OL,10,Fevidence in all the circumstances was
OL,11,Fcruel in the extreme.
OL,13,F"Today we stand with the victims of
OL,14,Fhis abuse and we salute their bravery
OL,15,Fand courage for speaking out."
OL,17,FThe MP for East Belfast said Donaldson
OL,18,Fmust "face the full force of the law".
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@^O]zD@FOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
