PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782224342
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"He also stands guilty of abusing and
OL,8,Fbetraying the trust placed in him by
OL,9,Fmany people over many years, including
OL,10,Fgood, honest colleagues in both our
OL,11,Fparty and the Ulster Unionist Party,
OL,12,Fas well as the wider community," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"It is now clear beyond doubt that he
OL,16,Fabused various positions of power over
OL,17,Fmany years since 1985 and has covered
OL,18,Fup his vile and manipulative behaviour.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
