PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782224342
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"We have been shocked by the evidence
OL,8,Fpresented, what we have heard reported
OL,9,Ffrom the court has been filthy and
OL,10,Fvile.
OL,12,F"For our part, we firmly believe in
OL,13,Fplacing our faith in the rule of law.
OL,15,F"For us, everyone is equal to the law
OL,16,Fand equally subject to it, no-one,
OL,17,Fregardless of their status or
OL,18,Fposition, can ever be above the law
OL,19,Fand Jeffrey Donaldson is no exception.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
