OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782224342
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson abused 'trust' of
OL,4,Cparty with 'vile' crimes, DUP leader
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Abuse, preying on the innocent and
OL,8,Ftaking advantage of the vulnerability
OL,9,Fof children in particular is evil.
OL,11,F"That Jeffrey Donaldson's lies and his
OL,12,Fcover-ups have been uncovered, and the
OL,13,Fspotlight of justice shone upon them,
OL,14,Fshould serve as a reminder that
OL,15,Fperpetrators cannot outrun justice.
OL,17,F"Victims can and must triumph over the
OL,18,Fevil darkness that pervaded their
OL,19,Finnocent lives."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU{D@PO]
